divs: Sighting DetailsI was at my home drinking hot tea when all the sudden my favorite indie rock station was interrupted with static. I looked out the window and saw a ufo. I told my mom and then I went to sleep. I slept that night with my limbs wrapped tight around my skateboard and my thrasher magazine incase the aliens came to get me. I woke up and all of my urban outfitter clothes were missing and i cried.
